* In {{ill|Bunroku|ja|文禄}} 1 (1592 AD), the campaign known as {{ill|Bunroku Campaign|ja|文禄・慶長の役#文禄の役|lt=Bunroku Campaign|lt_ja=文禄の役}} took place, which is known in Korea as the {{ill|Imjin War|ja|壬辰倭乱}}.

==壬辰)'s Months==
In a {{ill|Western calendar|ja|西暦}} year whose final digit is 1 or 6 (when the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干}} are {{ill|Sin|ja|辛}} and {{ill|Hei|ja|丙}}), the month of {{ill|March|ja|3月}} is designated as the {{ill|month (calendar)|ja|月 (暦)|lt=Month|lt_ja=月}} of {{ill|Renchin|ja|壬辰}}. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Old Calendar|ja|旧暦}} or to the {{ill|Seasonal Month|ja|節月}} (from {{ill|Qingming|ja|清明}} until the day before {{ill|Beginning of Summer|ja|立夏}}) as applicable.

