{{infobox Chinese|l=Yang Water Dragon|kanji=壬辰|romaji=mizunoe tatsu|onyomi=jishin|p=rénchén|w=jen-ch'en|mi=ʐən³⁵ ʈ͡ʂʰən|y=jam4 san4|j=jam4 san4|ci=jɐm sɐn|mc=ɲiɪm ɖin|oc-bs=ɲɨm ɖiŋ}}
{{Sexagenary cycle comprehensive}}
'''Yang Water Dragon also known as 壬辰''' (mizu no etatsu, jinsui no tatsu, jinshin) is one of the elements of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|六十干支|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}.

It is the 29th combination of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|六十干支|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, preceded by {{ill|Xinmao|ja|辛卯|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} and followed by {{ill|Guisi|ja|癸巳|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. In the framework of {{ill|Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|ja|陰陽五行思想|lt=Yin Yang Five Elements|lt_ja=陰陽五行|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} symbol {{ill|Ren|ja|壬|1=Mizunoe (壬)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} represents yang {{ill|Water|ja|水|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, while the {{ill|Earthly Branches|ja|十二支|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} symbol {{ill|Dragon|ja|辰|1=Dragon (zodiac)|lt=Dragon (辰)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} represents yang {{ill|Earth|ja|土|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, establishing a restraining relationship ({{ill|Mutual Restraint|ja|五行思想#相剋（そうこく）|lt=Mutual Restraint|lt_ja=相剋|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) (i.e. Earth overcomes Water).

==Yang Water Dragon (壬辰)'s Years==
A year in the {{ill|Western calendar|ja|西暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} that leaves a remainder of 32 when divided by 60 is a {{ill|year|ja|年|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} of {{ill|Renchin|ja|壬辰|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}.

That is, if a Western calendar year N (N>0) is a year of Renchin, then

<math> N - \lfloor{N/60}\rfloor * 60 = 32 </math>
Here, the symbol <math> \lfloor x \rfloor</math> denotes the {{ill|Floor function|ja|床関数|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}.

