===Events===
* In {{ill|Bunroku|ja|文禄|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1 (1592 AD), the campaign known as {{ill|Bunroku Campaign|ja|文禄・慶長の役#文禄の役|lt=Bunroku Campaign|lt_ja=文禄の役|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} took place, which is known in Korea as the {{ill|Imjin War|ja|壬辰倭乱|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}.

==Yang Water Dragon (壬辰)'s Months==
In a {{ill|Western calendar|ja|西暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} year whose final digit is 1 or 6 (when the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} are {{ill|Sin|ja|辛|1=Kanoto (辛)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} and {{ill|Hei|ja|丙|1=Hinoe (丙)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}), the month of {{ill|March|ja|3月|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} is designated as the {{ill|month (calendar)|ja|月 (暦)|lt=Month|lt_ja=月|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} of {{ill|Renchin|ja|壬辰|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} or to the {{ill|Seasonal Month|ja|節月|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (from {{ill|Qingming|ja|清明|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} until the day before {{ill|Beginning of Summer|ja|立夏|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) as applicable.

==Yang Water Dragon (壬辰)'s Days==
The {{ill|selected day|ja|選日|1=Senjitsu|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} for {{ill|Renchin|ja|壬辰|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} is as follows.
==={{nihongo|selection days|選日|senjitsu}}===
The day of {{ill|Renchin|ja|壬辰|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} is the 9th day of {{ill|Shihoumoku|ja|十方暮|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}.


