oken Sexagenary year|lt=2492 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2552 AD|ja|2552年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2552|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2552 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2612 AD|ja|2612年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2612|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2612 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2672 AD|ja|2672年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2672|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2672 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2732 AD|ja|2732年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2732|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2732 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2792 AD|ja|2792年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2792|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2792 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2852 AD|ja|2852年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2852|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2852 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2912 AD|ja|2912年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2912|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2912 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2972 AD|ja|2972年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2972|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2972 AD|qq=}} |}
===Events=== * In [[:en:Bunroku|Bunroku]] 1 (1592 AD), the campaign known as {{ill|Bunroku Campaign|ja|文禄・慶長の役#文禄の役|lt=Bunroku Campaign|lt_ja=文禄の役|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bunroku Campaign|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bunroku Campaign|qq=}} took place, which is known in Korea as the {{ill|Imjin War|ja|壬辰倭乱|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Imjin War|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Imjin War|qq=}}. ==Months of Yang Water Dragon== ==Yang Water Dragon (壬辰)'s Months== In a [[:en:Common Era|Common Era]] year whose final digit is 1 or 6 (when the [[:en:Heavenly Stems|Heavenly Stems]] are {{ill|Sin|ja|辛|1=Kanoto (辛)|lt=Kanoto (辛)|2=ja|3=辛|4=zh|5=辛|1=Kanoto (辛)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sin|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanoto (辛)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sin|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanoto (辛)|qq=}} and {{ill|Hei|ja|丙|1=Hinoe (丙)|lt=Hinoe (丙)|2=ja|3=丙|4=zh|5=丙|1=Hinoe (丙)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hei|13=User:Immanuelle/Hinoe (丙)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hei|13=User:Immanuelle/Hinoe (丙)|qq=}}), the month of [[:en:March|March]] is designated as the [[:en:Month|Month]] of {{ill|Renchin|ja|1=Yang Water Dragon|2=ja|壬辰|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Renchin|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Renchin|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Water Dragon|qq=}}. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} or to the [[:en:Solar term|Solar term]] (from [[:en:Qingming (solar term)|Qingming]] until the day before [[:en:Lixia|Lixia]]) as applicable. ==Days of Yang Water Dragon== ==Yang Water Dragon (壬辰)'s Days== The {{ill|selected day|ja|選日|1=Senjitsu|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/selected day|13=User:Immanuelle/Senjitsu|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/selected day|13=User:Immanuelle/Senjitsu|qq=}} for {{ill|Renchin|ja|1=Yang Water Dragon|2=ja|壬辰|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Renchin|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Renchin|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Water Dragon|qq=}} is as follows. ==={{nihongo|selection days|選日|senjitsu|qq=}}=== The day of {{ill|Renchin|ja|1=Yang Water Dragon|2=ja|壬辰|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Renchin|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Renchin|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Water Dragon|qq=}} is the 9th day of {{ill|Shihoumoku|ja|十方暮|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shihoumoku|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shihoumoku|qq=}}.
